&lt;p>One of the best teams I ever worked in had this concept embedded in the individuals.
There were no formal roles, everyone was a Senior Software Engineer.
But all three roles—Pioneer, Settler, and Townplanner—were clearly present.
Everyone had their part.
This organic distribution of roles was a key factor in the team&amp;rsquo;s success.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>